We Play Here Tour with Arthur Miguel is fast approaching, at dahil love na love namin kayo, may inihanda kaming surprise for all of you sa lahat ng tour stops! 🪢

𝐅𝐎𝐑 𝐄𝐕𝐄𝐑𝐘 𝐓𝐎𝐔𝐑 𝐒𝐓𝐎𝐏 𝐆𝐄𝐓 𝐀 𝐂𝐇𝐀𝐍𝐂𝐄 𝐓𝐎: 

💌 𝐃𝐄𝐃𝐈𝐂𝐀𝐓𝐄 𝐓𝐀𝐍𝐆𝐈𝐍𝐆 𝐈𝐊𝐀𝐖

- Go to the link/Scan the QR code and fill out the form to register
- ⁠One (1) lucky fan will be chosen for each tour stop
- Chosen fans will be contacted through social media so make sure your accounts are set to public
- ⁠The chosen fans will be called on stage to share/dedicate a message and the live performance of "Tanging Ikaw" to their special someone
- ⁠They will also receive an exclusive gift from Sugarcane 

Warner Music Philippines
Squidball na yan eh, anong palag namin dyan 😪 Secure your tickets na folks! Kita-kita tayo sa Elements 2025: UP Fair! ❤️‍🔥

CEBU!! 📢

Tara sa Cebu, Cebu-hay mo ayie 🤪 Kita kita tayo sa Ayala Malls Central Bloc, folks! ❤️‍🔥

SugarFolks 𝐂𝐨𝐦𝐦𝐮𝐧𝐢𝐭𝐲 𝐇𝐚𝐧𝐠𝐨𝐮𝐭 𝐏𝐚𝐫𝐭 𝟐? 👀

Nag promise kami dati na magkakaroon tayo ng hugot hangouts ulit para sa mga di nakapunta last time, baka ito na ang panahon para tuparin ‘yun! 💞

Pero para malaman namin if game talaga kayo sa 𝐇𝐮𝐠𝐨𝐭 𝐇𝐚𝐧𝐠𝐨𝐮𝐭𝐬 𝟐.𝟎, create a TikTok/IG Reels video using the official audio of “Tanging Ikaw”, and don’t forget to use the hashtag #𝐓𝐚𝐧𝐠𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐈𝐤𝐚𝐰𝐒𝐮𝐠𝐚𝐫𝐜𝐚𝐧𝐞

☑️: 𝐀𝐥𝐥 𝐜𝐨𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐬 𝐚𝐫𝐞 𝐚𝐜𝐜𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐞; whether it’s a dance choreo, live performance video of Sugarcane playing “Tanging Ikaw”, skits, or any creative ideas you have in mind

𝐎𝐧𝐥𝐢𝐧𝐞 𝐭𝐢𝐜𝐤𝐞𝐭 𝐩𝐮𝐫𝐜𝐡𝐚𝐬𝐞𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭: https://youthfest.helixpay.ph

𝐏𝐡𝐲𝐬𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥 𝐭𝐢𝐜𝐤𝐞𝐭 𝐩𝐮𝐫𝐜𝐡𝐚𝐬𝐞𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭 from 𝐃𝐁 𝐌𝐚𝐛𝐚𝐥𝐚𝐜𝐚𝐭'𝐬 𝐜𝐚𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐞𝐫 or through their 𝐬𝐞𝐥𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐞𝐝 𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐧𝐞𝐫 𝐬𝐜𝐡𝐨𝐨𝐥𝐬:
• 𝐃𝐨𝐧 𝐁𝐨𝐬𝐜𝐨 𝐀𝐜𝐚𝐝𝐞𝐦𝐲 𝐁𝐚𝐜𝐨𝐥𝐨𝐫
